773
00:48:26,612 --> 00:48:27,779
ask

774
00:48:29,364 --> 00:48:31,074
Will you listen to me?

775
00:48:32,993 --> 00:48:36,371
(Satoko) Yeah, I understand.

776
00:48:39,625 --> 00:48:42,669
Maybe you found a magic box?

777
00:48:43,295 --> 00:48:45,964
(Kinuko) Yeah...I think so.

778
00:48:56,308 --> 00:48:57,851
(Kinuko) Hehehehe...

779
00:48:59,686 --> 00:49:03,940
I'm really glad I asked you both.

780
00:49:06,902 --> 00:49:08,362
thank you

781
00:49:10,572 --> 00:49:12,574
♪～

